name: not started
definition: not started is the status of a process that is predicted to exist but has not yet begun.

name: cancelled
definition: cancelled is a process status in which the process, while planned to occur, will not occur.

name: planned
definition: planned is a process status for a process that has not yet started, but is referred to in a plan.

name: aborted
definition: aborted is a process status in which a started process will not complete as intended.

name: suspended
definition: suspended is the status of a process that is no longer progressing towards completion.

name: ongoing
definition: ongoing is the status of a process that is not yet complete.

name: completed
definition: completed is that status of a process that successfully unfolds.
